%% MyAIStorybook - System Sequence Diagram: Voice Input Story Generation Scenario

sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant System as :System
    
    Note over User,System: Voice Input Story Generation Scenario (Main Success)<br/>System is treated as BLACK BOX
    
    User->>System: makeNewStory()
    
    User->>System: recordVoiceInput()
    System-->>User: recording_started
    
    User->>System: stopRecording(audio_data)
    System-->>User: transcription(text)
    
    User->>System: confirmPrompt(confirmed_text)
    System-->>User: prompt_confirmed
    
    User->>System: selectOptions(generate_images, mode)
    
    User->>System: generateStory()
    System-->>User: story_with_images(title, scenes[], images[])
    
    Note right of System: System converts voice to text internally<br/>using Speech-to-Text<br/>Then proceeds with normal generation
